{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase funding for investment in 3G football pitches ",
        "additional_details": "We believe it is an absolute must that investment is made into this sector and needs to come from the Government. I speak for many when I describe the impact it is having on our children, when we are all looking forward to a game on the weekend and then it is called off following a pitch inspection. Some teams go weeks without playing a single game and it\u2019s upsetting for many kids who mentally rely on this social interaction. Please consider our children and our future.",
        "background": "Many grassroots football fixtures have been postponed due to grass pitches being in poor, unplayable condition. Many grassroots clubs do not have enough facilities available to accommodate the games.",
